  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/d662c7d8e9b5416bff4705e2ab8e829f.webp?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supply Kill-BOI 9000 with your enemies' hearts, so he can gain power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/98076526b8d4ffd2c6894375dfdef264.poster.avif?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/98076526b8d4ffd2c6894375dfdef264.webm?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/98076526b8d4ffd2c6894375dfdef264.mp4?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/15af4721b660bb610c5f3d32669ea047.webp?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drones that have circling saws? Sure!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grenades that contain Black Holes? Of course!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Burning cannonballs? Hell yeah!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/452ed0b939656eca5d77733d7d1f9422.poster.avif?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/452ed0b939656eca5d77733d7d1f9422.webm?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/452ed0b939656eca5d77733d7d1f9422.mp4?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/d65fbfcbb080ae13aeec33cd5dc855df.webp?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull on Kill-BOI's lever to win awesome gear for your human!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/9853c25d66e74591a0de22a67e493f2a.poster.avif?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/9853c25d66e74591a0de22a67e493f2a.webm?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/9853c25d66e74591a0de22a67e493f2a.mp4?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/96be21c45d9ed0f9eed0c8373ccbf428.webp?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with a friend in local Co-op (requires a friend).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/8c51793143f86d5fd79eef05b81f6db6.poster.avif?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/8c51793143f86d5fd79eef05b81f6db6.webm?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/8c51793143f86d5fd79eef05b81f6db6.mp4?t=1728890054\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2126400/extras/3ff757702bd0bc0bd2bcaa9937dd0a79.webp?t=1728890054\" width=600 height=40 /></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create a unique build every run with different combinations of weapons, upgrades and lots of weapon crossovers. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Survive for 10 minutes, then enter endless mode and try to come farther than any other human in the world! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Equip your human with hats, body armor and weapons with unique effects </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore the Wasteland, the Jungle and the Moon </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sustain through challenging weather events </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Master the game to survive Hard Mode! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Collect achievements!</p></li></ul>",
